   Incident News / The Pago Pago Home Page
   Pago Pago

      Welcome to the Pago Pago website! It contains information provided and
      approved by the Unified Command for this incident, and posted on the
      site as it becomes available. This website focuses on natural resource
      restoration efforts at fishing vessel grounding sites on coral reefs in
      American Samoa. The vessels were grounded during a severe storm on
      December 10, 1991. Natural resource trustees are conducting the
      restoration efforts, following U.S. Coast Guard response efforts.

